    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for your next favorite ride? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and let me tell you, it\u2019s been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in wonderful shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. Whether you\u2019re commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to hit the road with you. It\u2019s reliable, drives like a dream, and is just waiting for a new home. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
