    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a high-precision Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This chassis maintains exceptional torsional rigidity with a documented subframe reinforcement and a refreshed VANOS system for optimal cam timing. The mechanical limited-slip differential provides predictable lock-up, while the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension offer tactile feedback through every apex. This driver-focused example exhibits a healthy compression ratio and crisp throttle response, making it a mechanically sound investment for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
