    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun to drive? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, with just the right amount of character for a well-loved vehicle. It runs like a dream and is totally ready for your next road trip or daily commute! Come take it for a spin; I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 33500.0,
