    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit benefits from a comprehensive double VANOS overhaul and recent valve clearance adjustment, ensuring optimal volumetric efficiency. Power is channeled through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional longitudinal traction. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates to mitigate fatigue, while the suspension geometry is maintained via refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. The individual throttle bodies provide an immediate transient throttle response that defines this era of naturally aspirated engineering. While displaying minor cosmetic patina indicative of its service life, the structural and mechanical integrity remains uncompromising for the discerning driver.",
